<li><span id="CITEREFChandrasekharan1974" class="citation book">Chandrasekharan, K. R. (1974). <i>Bhabani Bhattacharya</i>. Indian Writers Series <b>7</b>. Arnold-Heinemann Publishers. <a href="/wiki/OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.worldcat.org/oclc/1176569">1176569</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABhabani+Bhattacharya&amp;rft.au=Chandrasekharan%2C+K.+R.&amp;rft.aufirst=K.+R.&amp;rft.aulast=Chandrasekharan&amp;rft.btitle=Bhabani+Bhattacharya&amp;rft.date=1974&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F1176569&amp;rft.pub=Arnold-Heinemann+Publishers&amp;rft.series=Indian+Writers+Series&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.volume=7" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
