<li><i>The Serpent and the Rope</i> by <a href="/wiki/Raja_Rao" title="Raja Rao">Raja Rao</a> (1964)</li>
<li><i>The Tribal World of Verrier Elwin</i> by <a href="/wiki/Verrier_Elwin" title="Verrier Elwin">Verrier Elwin</a> (1965)</li>
