<li><i><a href="/wiki/Morning_Face" title="Morning Face">Morning Face</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Mulk_Raj_Anand" title="Mulk Raj Anand">Mulk Raj Anand</a> (1971)</li>
<li><i>Scholar Extraordinary</i> by <a href="/wiki/Nirad_C._Chaudhuri" title="Nirad C. Chaudhuri">Nirad C. Chaudhuri</a> (1975)</li>
